responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "1A0D42604EF40D2425873697E53EB9FC", "I was not asking. As a regular in the Settler Militia you do as your commanded. You are to report to Sergeant Blackwood, the guard I stationed in the Briarmoor. He has been outmanned for quite some time. Be swift! For greater glory.")
